name: Vault of Stars - Demo
summary: The living constellations of the Guardians have long served as a shield against the emptiness and entropy of the Void. But the Void’s corruption has seeped into the Vault of Stars, drawn by the evils of humanity, encouraged by the Voidbringer. The stars have fallen to the Island of Souls, shattering the World Tree and plunging the world into darkness. The constellations have risen again as unholy shadows.
